{"tid":2190331,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有冇發覺次次外地發生抗爭, 總會有班人踩香港人廢??","createTime":"2020-09-05T14:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T19:26:13.000Z","uid":53705,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7c0dcee99b9260c22b0ab5e2760f9aecd0af324a","tid":2190331,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:21:38.000Z","msg":"我發覺每次外地發生抗爭, 就算係好和平既示威<br />\n都總會有班人踩香港人廢<br />\n例如, 加泰, 黎巴嫩, 白羅斯, 內蒙<br />\n一旦發生抗爭<br />\n<br />\n就會有一班踩港撚, 跳出來踩香港人<br />\n例如:「睇下人地幾勁 幾團結.....相反香港人 根本唔識反抗, 廢物」<br />\n<br />\n好似完全無視左 上年香港幾乎每個星期都有街頭戰鬥<br />\n示威者 同防暴隊激戰既場面<br />\n<br />\n而且外國示威者 好多時面對 只有警棍既防暴隊, 都只係推推撞撞<br />\n踩港撚 又即刻跳出來話人地一日 等於香港人搞一年<br />\n屌, 上年示威者 面對既防暴隊 有齊催淚彈 橡膠子彈, 水炮車, 結果示威者都可以頂住向前推進<br />\n<br />\n到底呢班人係咩心態?? <br />\n想踩香港人, 踩低香港人既士氣??"},{"pid":"8ef395c9e67f82c7e12d7ab8f1eb2840374a7d38","tid":2190331,"uid":177213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:23:12.000Z","msg":"冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似下面呢個Po咁講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成日話香港人廢個班人好撚煩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2149940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2149940</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1545b38a48721e26bac116e17b46d0a5f5321aab","tid":2190331,"uid":177213,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:25:24.000Z","msg":"1970年，蘇聯KGB特工Yuri Bezmenov叛變（無中譯，Google譯做 尤里&middot;貝茲諾夫），投靠美國，並公開蘇聯情報部門顛覆敵對國家社會嘅方法。由意志敗壞（demoralisation）開始，令到整個社會感到無助，唔團結，冷感，撕裂，以致崩潰，不戰而敗。呢套理論有學名，叫「顛覆」Subversion，而達到顛覆嘅行爲，就叫做 active measures / активные мероприятия。<br />\n<br />\n2019年，中華人民共和國依舊行使同一套理論，務求不需派兵嘅情況之下，摧毀香港。<br />\n<br />\n以下係英文原版，<ins>RedDragon1</ins>會員詳盡中文譯本，以及Yuri本人嘅lecture（好詳細，但係暫時未有中文字幕）：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/205241_7eea6806b9c2a3bab5e96198f70d917e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F205241_7eea6806b9c2a3bab5e96198f70d917e.jpg&h=c3fd5f15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/205438_6bb1532c022cdb6ed10001288a80bda1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F205438_6bb1532c022cdb6ed10001288a80bda1.png&h=0c922310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/205441_eca53b7aef1269d4e21df75d11908a82.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F205441_eca53b7aef1269d4e21df75d11908a82.png&h=0f49324e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/205444_59918a579714f06bf86dd55fa6157ee5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F205444_59918a579714f06bf86dd55fa6157ee5.png&h=ac452608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/205447_f2bfa51a29ba3b681f120a59fa01ea77.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F205447_f2bfa51a29ba3b681f120a59fa01ea77.png&h=4039f17c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPDF link: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1AZBfKokD65LfA7e7g1gil-K_CcSrl0eS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1AZBfKokD65LfA7e7g1gil-K_CcSrl0eS&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=286866a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1AZBfKokD65LfA7e7g1gil-K_CcSrl0eS</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SZnkULuWFDg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSZnkULuWFDg&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=edea5a6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SZnkULuWFDg</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n如果你冇時間睇哂成段lecture，個圖最後兩個顛覆步驟冇講清楚：<br />\n<br />\n「危機」係指令到社會運作嘅機器失效，即係銀行停止發票，立法會停止會議，法院不能夠再審判。同時間，另類政府組織會冒起，如人民法院。<br />\n<br />\n「危機」未直接入「正常化」之前有可能會走兩條路：國際介入（多國戰爭），or內戰。但係如果冇呢兩樣嘢發生嘅話，就會直接入最後一步：<br />\n<br />\n「正常化」，係指「社會動盪被入侵者完全制止」，蘇聯嘅例子係俄羅斯坦克車入城，<span class=\"red\">將原本親蘇聯嘅內奸、政客殺哂（因爲已經冇利用價值）</span>，由外來嘅俄羅斯人清洗一切反抗聲音，「正常化」個動盪。"},{"pid":"ab1022a731a13264d91aaa91b514ae0a2e7a7a02","tid":2190331,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"香港班差佬已經嚴重路法西效應，香港人頂到咁嘅武力成年唔係簡單<br />\n<br />\n但慢慢唔係出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b9bac3ffbf333f45226d63837f1bf13016fc69","tid":2190331,"uid":60321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:34:46.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"1c363cb682a3317b099ab76bc931f7a8cdf56a15","tid":2190331,"uid":72457,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"因為香港人真係廢<br />\n完"},{"pid":"87df96b27151797248f2ed7af61e24ed7a0e2e48","tid":2190331,"uid":204429,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:36:51.000Z","msg":"緊係廢啦 你睇人地企前線個班全部都係大人黎 香港反而係班口靚仔企前線？你話抵唔抵屌<br />\n<br />\n利申 大家都係垃圾 包括我"},{"pid":"7fbc88fea8a2b71b8dc8c2cfcca95e68110dca5c","tid":2190331,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"87df96b27151797248f2ed7af61e24ed7a0e2e48","tid":2190331,"uid":204429,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:36:51.000Z","msg":"緊係廢啦 你睇人地企前線個班全部都係大人黎 香港反而係班口靚仔企前線？你話抵唔抵屌<br />\n<br />\n利申 大家都係垃圾 包括我"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:48:38.000Z","msg":"香港係玩分工<br />\n<br />\n後生仔 精力充沛, 所以企前面<br />\n成年人 已經無左活力, 但有錢, 可以提供物資, 搞後勤"},{"pid":"1ebb91a375284e506c1653c768ec45a0c5c96a56","tid":2190331,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ab1022a731a13264d91aaa91b514ae0a2e7a7a02","tid":2190331,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"香港班差佬已經嚴重路法西效應，香港人頂到咁嘅武力成年唔係簡單<br />\n<br />\n但慢慢唔係出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:49:46.000Z","msg":"重點係 香港防暴隊 既武器, 幾乎是世界最頂級<br />\n人地美國, 法國, 果D防暴裝備, 都無香港果班咁精良<br />\n<br />\n如果香港人打得嬴香港防暴, 理論上已經可以打嬴世界好多防暴隊"},{"pid":"ce94b4701041fc95016d00059dd9ee460bcf50d7","tid":2190331,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1c363cb682a3317b099ab76bc931f7a8cdf56a15","tid":2190331,"uid":72457,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"因為香港人真係廢<br />\n完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"如果香港人係廢<br />\n<br />\n咁白羅斯人, 加泰人, 法國黃背心 都係廢"},{"pid":"602898375e2682e2c2f33a57b53b29c85737f4fe","tid":2190331,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7fbc88fea8a2b71b8dc8c2cfcca95e68110dca5c","tid":2190331,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"87df96b27151797248f2ed7af61e24ed7a0e2e48","tid":2190331,"uid":204429,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:36:51.000Z","msg":"緊係廢啦 你睇人地企前線個班全部都係大人黎 香港反而係班口靚仔企前線？你話抵唔抵屌<br />\n<br />\n利申 大家都係垃圾 包括我"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:48:38.000Z","msg":"香港係玩分工<br />\n<br />\n後生仔 精力充沛, 所以企前面<br />\n成年人 已經無左活力, 但有錢, 可以提供物資, 搞後勤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:51:44.000Z","msg":"所以會送頭既任務就留返俾後生仔做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187afbc069cd6b5261e1174d48fb33a10f3d9e0c","tid":2190331,"uid":240890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"睇直播 <br />\n人地國家防暴同示威都<br />\n大家可以企到勁近都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e657e8f0e1d37b17dc6b229afe27ba325419bd3","tid":2190331,"uid":85556,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7fbc88fea8a2b71b8dc8c2cfcca95e68110dca5c","tid":2190331,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"87df96b27151797248f2ed7af61e24ed7a0e2e48","tid":2190331,"uid":204429,"like":1,"dis