搞左咁多年都無人關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港搞左一年已經助攻蔡英文，上咗美國總統大選議題，拆穿哂中共大外宣，引起歐洲日本圍共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話我哋廢個d人只係成日想一步登天又唔付出<br />\n真係有參與抗爭組織嘅就知熱度無停過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23b972a436d1a2c301409c754b6a5d86bf1a0cb","tid":2190331,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T15:11:24.000Z","msg":"士氣都幾重要"},{"pid":"d064db25dc0ab83792c85154e1cd567be07b3bc4","tid":2190331,"uid":16057,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce94b4701041fc95016d00059dd9ee460bcf50d7","tid":2190331,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1c363cb682a3317b099ab76bc931f7a8cdf56a15","tid":2190331,"uid":72457,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"因為香港人真係廢<br />\n完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"如果香港人係廢<br />\n<br />\n咁白羅斯人, 加泰人, 法國黃背心 都係廢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T15:17:19.000Z","msg":"香港人點會廢 <br />\n<br />\n上述啲國家既人一早有個國民身份認同 敢為自己既國家犧牲 但香港人呢個身份認同 客觀啲講都係呢一兩年先真係成左個雛形 香港人係呢一兩年做既野真係已經好勁好叻 <br />\n唔好忘記香港人面對緊支共呢個全世界最識打壓人民既恐怖分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話香港人廢根本純粹放負 忽視客觀現實"},{"pid":"6c136022bdd1d45693d5e8516da234adb6bbb3a3","tid":2190331,"uid":58089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T15:19:41.000Z","msg":"好多都係五毛pr為講而講"},{"pid":"f78764353208ddec6c0baad8df8742a5e72cd04a","tid":2190331,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T19:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wqtoUVX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwqtoUVX.jpg&h=81a84daa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29d2aba354d03783b9cc59814b6525894dad06b4","tid":2190331,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c0dcee99b9260c22b0ab5e2760f9aecd0af324a","tid":2190331,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:21:38.000Z","msg":"我發覺每次外地發生抗爭, 就算係好和平既示威<br />\n都總會有班人踩香港人廢<br />\n例如, 加泰, 黎巴嫩, 白羅斯, 內蒙<br />\n一旦發生抗爭<br />\n<br />\n就會有一班踩港撚, 跳出來踩香港人<br />\n例如:「睇下人地幾勁 幾團結.....相反香港人 根本唔識反抗, 廢物」<br />\n<br />\n好似完全無視左 上年香港幾乎每個星期都有街頭戰鬥<br />\n示威者 同防暴隊激戰既場面<br />\n<br />\n而且外國示威者 好多時面對 只有警棍既防暴隊, 都只係推推撞撞<br />\n踩港撚 又即刻跳出來話人地一日 等於香港人搞一年<br />\n屌, 上年示威者 面對既防暴隊 有齊催淚彈 橡膠子彈, 水炮車, 結果示威者都可以頂住向前推進<br />\n<br />\n到底呢班人係咩心態?? <br />\n想踩香港人, 踩低香港人既士氣??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T19:20:58.000Z","msg":"五毛打擊士氣手法"},{"pid":"fe3070d07be1a05742c19a7e66002755f699cedc","tid":2190331,"uid":204429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd5f9509e161f70be44e4c7bcbc26c7d95549b14","tid":2190331,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e657e8f0e1d37b17dc6b229afe27ba325419bd3","tid":2190331,"uid":85556,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7fbc88fea8a2b71b8dc8c2cfcca95e68110dca5c","tid":2190331,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:48:38.000Z","msg":"香港係玩分工<br />\n<br />\n後生仔 精力充沛, 所以企前面<br />\n成年人 已經無左活力, 但有錢, 可以提供物資, 搞後勤"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T14:55:36.000Z","msg":"理想中係咁，但事實起碼八成成年人係有份出賣同推後生仔去死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T15:05:07.000Z","msg":"你呢D就係踩港心態<br />\n<br />\n踩緊香港成年人 無做過野, 拖後腳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T19:24:26.000Z","msg":"完<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HL1JUXL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHL1JUXL.png&h=2e1a3f91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49e6e485c355a1b627c0fbdab84415b163f94013","tid":2190331,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e657e8f0e1d37b17dc6b229afe27ba325419bd3","tid":2190331,"uid":85556,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7fbc88fea8a2b71b8dc8c2cfcca95e68110dca5c","tid":2190331,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"87df96b27151797248f2ed7af61e24ed7a0e2e48","tid":2190331,"uid":204429,